      <description>&lt;p&gt;2024년의 디지털 환경을 항해하면서, 사이버 보안 패러다임은 급격히 변화하고 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-ai-기반-공격-ai-driven-attacks&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;1. AI 기반 공격 (AI-Driven Attacks) &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#1-ai-%ea%b8%b0%eb%b0%98-%ea%b3%b5%ea%b2%a9-ai-driven-attacks&#34; aria-label=&#34;앵커&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;생성형 AI를 활용한 정교한 피싱 캠페인은 이제 진짜 통신과 구별할 수 없을 정도입니다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-공급망-취약점-supply-chain-vulnerabilities&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;2. 공급망 취약점 (Supply Chain Vulnerabilities) &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#2-%ea%b3%b5%ea%b8%89%eb%a7%9d-%ec%b7%a8%ec%95%bd%ec%a0%90-supply-chain-vulnerabilities&#34; aria-label=&#34;앵커&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;제3자 리스크 관리는 더 이상 선택 사항이 아닙니다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;결론&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;결론 &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%ea%b2%b0%eb%a1%a0&#34; aria-label=&#34;앵커&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;JE Tech Holdings는 귀사의 보안 태세에 대한 즉각적인 검토를 권장합니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
